<a class="cover" href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1350e486d20b077c0918a67b&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
<img class="cover-img" data-height="" data-width="" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/2934349b033b5bb526964f4d3bd3d539b700bcc4.jpg"/>
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"/></div>
<p class="title">
英国使团访华，口口声称没有领土野心，乾隆得知后却大怒
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1350e486d20b077c0918a67b&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
1792年，英国国王乔治三世派英国贵族马戛尔尼率领使团访华，希望双方能就贸易问题进行磋商，以实现互利。这就是清朝外交史上著名的“马戛尔尼使团访华”事件。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-12-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like" data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">153</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoid="a46e4d351635a503fffb9c30">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=85010534&amp;authorId=7a442b409fc30cc8e0b3fb26&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/c2fdfc039245d68895d3024eacc27d1ed31b2402.jpg"/></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>勇哥读史</strong>
<span>给你好看的历史</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a class="cover" href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a46e4d351635a503fffb9c30&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
<img class="cover-img" data-height="" data-width="" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/7af40ad162d9f2d3d1908592a5ec8a136227ccce.jpg"/>
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"/></div>
<p class="title">
乾隆帝送给此人一个槟榔荷包 他回报以一场屈辱战争
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=a46e4d351635a503fffb9c30&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
小斯当东的发言对下议院产生了至关重要的影响。在三天后的下议院投票中，主战派获得271票，反战派获得262票。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-04-07</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like" data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">128</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoid="045b9b900e7f73890832d884">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=09b1f993&amp;authorId=db3f0c114f8566d5057ca720&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/fcfaaf51f3deb48f247c7455fa1f3a292df57820.jpg"/></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>嘴哥闲谈</strong>
<span>关注中外逸闻秘史、探索神秘奇异事件</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a class="cover" href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=045b9b900e7f73890832d884&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
<img class="cover-img" data-height="" data-width="" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/ac345982b2b7d0a25f7b2333c0ef76094a369ae9.jpg"/>
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"/></div>
<p class="title">
200年前英国人跑到中国提了一堆要求，乾隆只一句话就怼回去了！
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=045b9b900e7f73890832d884&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
清朝初年开始就实行禁海了，据说是为了防止沿海人民与台湾的郑成功联系。对外的通商口岸仅澳门一处，因为这是葡萄牙人的地盘，硕果仅存的一个对外开放的地方。康熙年间平定台湾后，清政府才对禁海方面稍有松懈。彼时正是大航海时代，西方商船来华逐渐增多了。而这让清政府又开始有所防范，清政府...</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-11-24</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like" data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">72</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoid="db3f0c114e1a67d5057ca7b9">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=5b8d4b02&amp;authorId=287cbd9a64087baeaaf47020&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/1e30e924b899a901201fc6dc14950a7b0208f536.jpg"/></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>文史宴</strong>
<span>熟悉历史陌生化，陌生历史普及化</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a class="cover" href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=db3f0c114e1a67d5057ca7b9&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
<img class="cover-img" data-height="" data-width="" src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/4b90f603738da977b549c383bb51f8198618e330.jpg"/>
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"/></div>
<p class="title">
文史宴：马戛尔尼到底给乾隆跪了没有？跪了
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=db3f0c114e1a67d5057ca7b9&amp;lemmaId=1051262&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
乾隆与英国马戛尔尼的使团的会面，因礼仪之争不欢而散，乾隆的颟顸自大对中国近代的影响毋庸多言。但是从另一个角度看，乾隆作为一个精明的统治者，其表现也不完全是事出无因。胡小伟先生从当时的世界大势着眼，东西万里，信手拈来，发现这场会面不是那么简单。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-11-20</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like" data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">43</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
